{NORTH has 23 points and opens 2\C.

SOUTH, with 4 points, must respond 2\D.

NORTH now shows a \H suit (at least 5) by bidding 2\H.

SOUTH likes \Hs, she has already told NORTH she has fewer than 8 points, so she 
bids 4\H.}

