{EAST has lots of points - 26 to be exact. She opens 2\C. 
In the old days this hand would have been opened 3NT.

WEST has 4 points and responds 2\D.

EAST now shows her full strength by jumping to 3NT (25-27 points, balanced).

WEST knows there is no slam, so he passes 3NT.}

